  "title": "6 Month Contract Facilities Executive / Facilities Coordinator ( Healthcare ) Up 3.8K #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Executive, Facility Operations (6-Month Contract)</strong></p><p><strong>Sector:</strong> Healthcare / Facilities Management<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Contract (Convertible)<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $4,000 per month</p><p>This role supports daily facilities and operations within a healthcare environment, ensuring a safe, well-maintained, and efficient workplace for patients, staff, and visitors.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Coordinate facilities services including maintenance, housekeeping, security, and waste management</li><li>Conduct routine checks and follow up on maintenance and safety issues</li><li>Support procurement, contract administration, and inventory tracking</li><li>Liaise with vendors, contractors, and internal stakeholders on operational matters</li><li>Assist in safety activities, fire drills, audits, and compliance exercises</li><li>Support events and operational projects as required</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Diploma in Facilities Management, Operations, or a related field</li><li>Relevant experience in facilities or operations support; healthcare experience is an advantage</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please click “ APPLY NOW”<br /></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p>Whatsapp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/+6597430026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://wa.me/+6597430026</a>  </p><p>Email : <a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br /></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p></p>",
